{"tid":446202,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人而家仲鍾意玩舊版足球game","createTime":"2017-10-24T05:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T14:46:00.000Z","uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3eaba7c69c281bcd4486b623bc8375465917f167","tid":446202,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"我就鍾意玩pes2013，算係近年比較有水準嘅winning<br />\n而且AC米蘭仲有柏圖 (呢樣好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最正係杜奧巴同伊度奧都係冇球會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係伊度奧，球隊唔夠前鋒時真係強烈推薦買黎玩，非常實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下送上我隊宇宙級AC米蘭，拎過三冠王+柏圖一季入左32球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (利申：其實如果唔係我成日skip match可以再入多幾球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"6ba43977a46ee086c85407fff114b8e396eea4d3","tid":446202,"uid":90657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"FIFA Online<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175b50e580eb3b24276142df73471a4c07662173","tid":446202,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FIFA Online<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都玩過<br />\n但其實好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔課金又好難有頂級球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4511e5a94c8d5fffcf9459336c858ceae5d8a69","tid":446202,"uid":90657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>FIFA Online<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都玩過<br />\n但其實好悶<img src=\"/assets/fa